Class DirectoryServerInitializer.AdvertiserBridge

All Implemented Interfaces:

Enclosing class:
DirectoryServerInitializer
static class DirectoryServerInitializer.AdvertiserBridge
extends Object
implements Advertiser, CommandLogic

AdvertiserBridge provides the Advertiser QoS to clients. It implements the Bridge design pattern. It decouples the Advertiser abstraction from the implementation of Advertiser.

Usage and implementation note: Because of the way that the SOUSA framework discovers CommandLogics, using an instance of AdvertiserBridge instead of an instance of DirectoryServer_ControlLogic as an argument to IdolInitializer.addCommandLogic(CommandLogic) permits the hiding of the other interfaces that DirectoryServer_ControlLogic implements from the outside world. That's a good thing. We don't want the methods of Clock.AlarmHandler, for example, available via RMI.
